    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6337936/" class="title-link">专注、计划、效率</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6337936"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/55480699/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u55480699-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/55480699/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">洗洗睡吧YYH</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-10-19"
      class="main-meta">2013-10-19 21:28:33</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6337936_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  读完这本书的几点感想： 1.做任何事专注力很重要，不要轻易被打断，单线程完成好一件事； 2.做任何事要有可行的计划和目标，短时间内可实现的目标，会有成就感； 3.效率和做事方法很重要，学习别人的方法，提高效率。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
